    directly for things that only happen on your own screen.


    The CVR Interactable
    setup(see networked button setup) also works for local events, and it is especially
    useful because it allows you to drag multiple objects into its array list at
    once, which is much easier than adding them one by one.'
  url: 
  locked: 1
  type: 1
